<div class="title">Benzo Increase Effects?</div>
<div class="substance">2C-B & Diazepam (Valium)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Anubis&Exact=1">Anubis</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Anubis. "Benzo Increase Effects?: An Experience with 2C-B & Diazepam (Valium) (exp5854)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 24, 2001. erowid.org/exp/5854</div>

<br/>



